      <title>拨款法案通过后，期待 1 月份的“特朗普三连胜”：共和党众议员 Huizenga</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/looking-forward-to-trump-trifecta-says-rep-huizenga-video</link>
